### Base API Check
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Test Database Write
POST http://localhost:3000/api/test-db
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Entry",
  "message": "Writing this to Firestore from REST Client!"
}

### Add New Novel (Valid Draft Request)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/novel/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "test-novel-3",
  "author": "Rollie Garcia",
  "description": "test description.",
  "status": "draft",
  "metadata": {
    "tags": ["sci-fi", "adventure", "technology"],
    "coverImage": "https://example.com/covers.jpg",
    "totalWords": 5550
  },
  "episodes": [
    {
      "episodeNumber": 1,
      "title": "Episode 1: The First Compile",
      "summary": "Our protagonist boots the editor for the first time.",
      "published": false,
      "chapters": [
        {
          "chapterNumber": 1,
          "title": "Chapter 1:",
          "content": "In the beginning, there...",
          "wordCount": 2450,
          "notes": "Introductory chapter."
        },
        {
          "chapterNumber": 2,
          "title": "Chapter 2: hello",
          "content": "content-2",
          "wordCount": 3100,
          "notes": "Action-packed blablabla."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### Add New Novel (Validation Failure Example)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/novel/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "author": "Rollie Garcia",
  "status": "invalid-status"
}

### Add New Episode to Novel
POST http://localhost:3000/api/novel/replace_with_novel_id/episodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Episode 2: The Next Phase",
  "summary": "The journey continues into new territories.",
  "published": true,
  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapterNumber": 1,
      "title": "Chapter 1: The Arrival",
      "content": "They arrived at dawn...",
      "wordCount": 1500,
      "notes": "Remember to introduce the new character."
    }
  ]
}

### Get List of All Novels
GET http://localhost:3000/api/novel

### Get All Episodes in a Novel
GET http://localhost:3000/api/novel/replace_with_novel_id/episodes
